Let me write it out because I know

00:09:05.403 --> 00:09:07.572
this can be a little bit confusing

00:09:07.572 --> 00:09:09.020
the first time you see it.

00:09:09.020 --> 00:09:12.480
So six minus four factorial,

00:09:13.310 --> 00:09:16.102
factorial, which is equal to,

00:09:16.102 --> 00:09:21.082
which is equal to six
factorial over four factorial,

00:09:21.082 --> 00:09:25.296
over four factorial, times
this thing right over here

00:09:25.296 --> 00:09:28.523
is two factorial, times two factorial,

00:09:28.523 --> 00:09:31.169
which is going to be equal to, we can just

00:09:31.169 --> 00:09:34.907
write out the factorials,
six times five times four

00:09:34.907 --> 00:09:38.484
times three times two times one,

00:09:38.484 --> 00:09:41.142
over four.

00:09:41.804 --> 00:09:45.449
Four time three times two times one

00:09:45.449 --> 00:09:47.172
times,

00:09:47.725 --> 00:09:50.171
times two times one.

00:09:50.171 --> 00:09:53.018
Of course that's going
to cancel with that.

00:09:53.018 --> 00:09:55.340
Then the one doesn't
really change the value,

00:09:55.340 --> 00:09:57.906
so let me get rid of this one here.

00:09:57.906 --> 00:10:02.526
Let's see, this three can
cancel with this three.

00:10:02.526 --> 00:10:05.301
This four could cancel with this four.

00:10:05.301 --> 00:10:09.004
Then it's six divided by
